                  "excerpt": "Stacks with Aero Vantage for a total of -175% gravity. This has several odd effects on aerial momentum; when starting an Aim Glide while falling, the user will stop immediately and slightly rise, while when starting an Aim Glide while rising(such as from a Jump , Double Jump , or Bullet Jump ) the user will briefly fall before stabilizing in midair."
